message.content:
Before Cam broke his arm, in 5 minutes, he could type:

9 words/minute × 5 minutes = 45 words

After breaking his arm and typing with his left hand, in 5 minutes, he could type:

6 words/minute × 5 minutes = 30 words

The difference between the number of words typed before and after is:

45 words - 30 words = 15 words
